text: Anatoli Viktorovich Strokatov (born 1955), is a male former international table tennis player from the USSR. He won a silver medal at the 1973 World Table Tennis Championships in the mixed doubles with Asta Gedraitite. He also won three English Open titles. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:Soviet table tennis players Category:Ukrainian male table tennis players Category:Sportspeople from Lviv Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
